<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your StayZen Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 4px solid #000000;
            box-shadow: 12px 12px 0px #000000;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            color: #000000;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .otp-box {
            background-color: #FFE500;
            border: 3px solid #000000;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0px #000000;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            border-top: 2px solid #eeeeee;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>StayZen</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong><%= username %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to StayZen. Your journey to premium stays starts here. Please use the following code to verify your account:</p>
            
            <div class="otp-box">
                <%= otp %>
            </div>

            <p>This code will expire in 10 minutes. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The StayZen Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 StayZen Hospitality Group. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
